                                                <p>Arrive in the early morning at Lao Cai station, near the Chinese border; take a scenic drive to the hill station of Sapa. Enjoy the spectacular views of rice-terraced mountains and Black H’Mong and Red Dao hill tribe people dressed in their colorful wares walking along the roadside.</p>
